Where did my Google go?
Full list of Storm spam links found so far

Here is the full list of server URLs linked from Storm botnet spam (those I've found so far, of course). Many have already been fixed; those in bold are currently returning HTTP 200 responses, but many of those are actually placeholder pages and aren't actually malware any more.

Blocking these domains is probably not the best strategy.

This list is updated hourly. Servers still returning HTTP 200 responses are polled every four hours; after the first non-200 response, they're taken off the active list.

If you just want a list of the landing pages spammed, that's here.

And if you want a text list of all the domains still active, that's here (shout out to Dirk at 1&1 for suggesting this and single-handedly cleaning up 11.6% of them in one fell swoop!)
